text:
To contain #Coronavirus PM Abiy announced 10 point measures for the next 2 weeks: 
1. Large gatherings including sporting events are banned & small gatherings require Ministry of Health clearance.
2. All educational institutions except universities will be closed.
3. Religious institutions need to limit gatherings.
4. A national hygiene movement is launched.
5. Government allocated budget for hygiene & other necessities.
6. Government buses are to be availed free of charge to control crowding. Special buses are designated for public servants. Private transporters are also asked to follow suit.
7. Ministry of Trade will monitor & control prices on necessities.
8. Special attention will be given to the elderly.
9. Volunteers are asked to compliment on educating & preventing efforts.
10. All need to equip with accurate information from the Ministry of Health. #Ethiopia
